title: Take-home Exercise 1
text:
1. The Task
The task for take-home exercise 1 is to plot the age-sex pyramid for 9 selected area in Singapore to illustrate thedemographic structure of Singapore at planning area level.


2. The Data
Singapore Residents by Planning Area / Subzone, Age Group, Sex and Type of Dwelling, June 2022 from Department of Statistics, Singapore is used to display 9 planning area.
